{"tid":2389759,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[南非一通] 為了重新啟用 Flash 支持，南非稅務局發佈了自己的 Web 瀏覽器","createTime":"2021-02-01T06:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T11:44:08.000Z","uid":205377,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec13c7fc3cccb5aaf18a6a2cf4911ad1979e1b71","tid":2389759,"uid":205377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.linux.net.cn/data/attachment/album/202102/01/124826mfvayosycvcofytt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.linux.net.cn%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Falbum%2F202102%2F01%2F124826mfvayosycvcofytt.jpg&h=0f0bc589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據 zdnet 報導稱，南非稅務局發佈這個定製瀏覽器的&ldquo;唯一的目的是重新啟用 Adobe Flash Player 支持，而不是將其現有的網站從使用 Flash 移植到基於 HTML 的網頁表單中。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n該機構稱自己&ldquo;受到定時炸彈機制的影響&rdquo;，從 Flash 停用的當天開始，該機構無法通過網站接收任何報稅信息，而上傳的表單被設計成 Flash 小部件。儘管有三年半的先機，南非稅務局並沒有選擇將其 Flash 小部件移植到基本的 HTML 和 JS 表單中。相反，他們決定採取一個在 IT 決策史上最令人瞠目結舌的錯誤決定，發佈自己的 Web 瀏覽器[2]。<br />\n<br />\n該瀏覽器是 Chromium 瀏覽器的簡化版，有兩個功能：第一個是重新啟用 Flash 支持。第二是讓用戶&ldquo;能且只能&rdquo;訪問南非稅務局的官方網站。並且，該瀏覽器只有 Windows 版本。<br />\n<br />\n當然，這麼有&ldquo;創舉&rdquo;的事情，也絕非南非稅務局一家，ZDnet 也提到了中國大連有了類似的&ldquo;解決方案[3]&rdquo;。我覺得，很快就會有其它的機構&ldquo;有樣學樣&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://www.zdnet.com/article/south-african-government-releases-its-own-browser-just-to-re-enable-flash-support/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zdnet.com%2Farticle%2Fsouth-african-government-releases-its-own-browser-just-to-re-enable-flash-support%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=12f09c8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zdnet.com/article/south-african-government-releases-its-own-browser-just-to-re-enable-flash-support/</a><br />\n南非稅局個browser ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sarstax/status/1353699405912797184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsarstax%2Fstatus%2F1353699405912797184&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=fda27acb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsarstax%2Fstatus%2F1353699405912797184&h=0d1356c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sarstax/status/1353699405912797184</a><br />\n<br />\n我記得台灣有間廠都出左個好少少既solution :<a href=\"https://www.puffin.com/flash-store/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.puffin.com%2Fflash-store%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=0796c966\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.puffin.com/flash-store/</a>"},{"pid":"b07ed835adfbc2da6c40207279c6ee87c8bcd531","tid":2389759,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:18:28.000Z","msg":"支国有自己OS添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9700d1c0209ef7ec75505cd55c7c0cbef7f996","tid":2389759,"uid":200317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"用幾倍人力做啲冇成效嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651b53f8a921bc4c2f7634d113073b9a6ab4916e","tid":2389759,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab9700d1c0209ef7ec75505cd55c7c0cbef7f996","tid":2389759,"uid":200317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"用幾倍人力做啲冇成效嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:24:22.000Z","msg":"可能人地計過度過update成part野仲貴呢"},{"pid":"d000baca1769435d50af40ddcb71110672d20da3","tid":2389759,"uid":200317,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"651b53f8a921bc4c2f7634d113073b9a6ab4916e","tid":2389759,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab9700d1c0209ef7ec75505cd55c7c0cbef7f996","tid":2389759,"uid":200317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"用幾倍人力做啲冇成效嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-0